- Make generic module have ability for processing

- Modules
	- Encoder
	- Decoder 
	- Waveforms

- Sequencer

- Arguments (argp)
	- Volume control for each module
	- Channel control for each module
	- Lifetime control for each module
	- FM Synth waveform specification

- IPC daemon
	- runtime updating of effects,
	- ability to set up multiple input streams for a merge module
	- creation of a config format to specify process configurations
